      "content": "that's a good start. can u expand on the part about 'systemic repair'? i want to hit hard on why the idea of meritocracy is basically just a way to ignore the reality of how systemic racism works. like, how do i frame meritocracy as being fundamentally incompatible with true racial equity?",
